{"tid":2239757,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"今年七一或之後受聘公務員　須宣誓或聲明擁護基本法","createTime":"2020-10-12T07:54:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T08:11:15.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"497ee5e08d3fa64dc52eae45fd41ffd709074a10","tid":2239757,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:54:22.000Z","msg":"公務員事務局今日向各部門發出通告，公布今年7月起聘任為公務員的人士，將要宣誓或作出聲明擁護《基本法》、效忠香港特區和對香港特區政府負責。<br />\n<br />\n當局指出，大部分準受聘人須在接受聘任時同時簽署聲明；至於直接受聘擔任高級職位如部門首長的人士則須宣誓，以加強公務員對其公職身份帶來的期望和責任的認知。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554242-20201012.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554242-20201012.htm&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBVScv4UPbHgCWRxxYzHlmUY%3D&h=0936d9c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554242-20201012.htm&h=e0f34703\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554242-20201012.htm</a>"},{"pid":"474e55f052ee69c0666c4dd28f24d05fb9cefbdf","tid":2239757,"uid":15010,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T08:01:46.000Z","msg":"宣左對移民有冇影響"},{"pid":"79e8d3ed5023057f35affc00fb9a8ac860c16570","tid":2239757,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T08:03:32.000Z","msg":"就算仆街啲迫埋aco 都要宣誓<br />\n<br />\n咪一樣幾萬人報名爭住做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"977e5bae2a88364970529ad9f9c5bbdfcebffba0","tid":2239757,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"474e55f052ee69c0666c4dd28f24d05fb9cefbdf","tid":2239757,"uid":15010,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T08:01:46.000Z","msg":"宣左對移民有冇影響"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T08:03:44.000Z","msg":"上班台連登仔話冇，繼續放心做公務員"},{"pid":"1fe4b406d06e1a725f160db70954511ff5786b5a","tid":2239757,"uid":292131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"474e55f052ee